public boolean isForwardAll()
If true, then all WebSocket communication is forwarded, but not stored in database, nor shown in user interface.

Returns:
True if all traffic should only be forwarded.

isBreakOnPingPong

public boolean isBreakOnPingPong()
If false, then no PING/PONG messages are caught when:
  • enabled break on all requests/responses buttons are enabled
  • stepping through to next request/response

Returns:
True if it should break also on ping & pong messages.

isBreakOnAll

public boolean isBreakOnAll()
If true, then WebSocket messages are caught when break on all requests/responses is active. Otherwise WebSocket communication is skipped.

Returns:
True if it should break on all HTTP requests/responses.
